---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="Usic" description="The Circle of Colors — Twelve keys mapped to landscape. The Mas Thesis.">

<section class="usic-hero">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="usic-eyebrow mono">The Circle of Colors</div>
    <h1 class="usic-title">Usic</h1>
    <p class="usic-sub">Twelve keys mapped to landscape. Seven natural keys inhale. Five sharp keys exhale. Piralus at the center. Each key holds a region, an ecosystem, a color, and a tone.</p>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="usic-center">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="piralus-card">
      <div class="piralus-label mono">Center</div>
      <h2 class="piralus-name">Piralus</h2>
      <p class="piralus-desc">The mountain at the center. Named from O'Shin by a sea captain who never climbed it. Every key wedge radiates from here.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="usic-keys">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="keys-label mono">Natural keys — inhale (7)</div>
    <div class="keys-grid">

      <div class="key-card" style="--kc:#E53327">
        <div class="key-badge mono">C</div>
        <div class="key-color-bar"></div>
        <div class="key-color-name mono">Red</div>
        <h3 class="key-range">The Heart → Quiets Source Forest</h3>
        <p class="key-desc">Home. Low Queen Qualia's domain. Interior to muted edge where Ecila drains and Ceila nurtures.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="key-card" style="--kc:#31A048">
        <div class="key-badge mono">G</div>
        <div class="key-color-bar"></div>
        <div class="key-color-name mono">Green</div>
        <h3 class="key-range">Quiets → Keylock</h3>
        <p class="key-desc">Interior river to coast gate. The hinge between forest and coast. Kalaloch is Keylock — the lock that opens.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="key-card" style="--kc:#D43259">
        <div class="key-badge mono">D</div>
        <div class="key-color-bar"></div>
        <div class="key-color-name mono">Pink</div>
        <h3 class="key-range">Darkive Source Forest → Trap Island</h3>
        <p class="key-desc">Data enters the system, routes to Piralus. D begins the D-A-E coastal run — the shore that spells its own keys. D to E = DarkivE.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="key-card" style="--kc:#ECD31B">
        <div class="key-badge mono">A</div>
        <div class="key-color-bar"></div>
        <div class="key-color-name mono">Yellow</div>
        <h3 class="key-range">Source Forest → Sh'Doot</h3>
        <p class="key-desc">Rain forest to convergence. Trip's lighthouse. Mr. Normal is the agent. Yellow = sunlight that burns and powers simultaneously.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="key-card" style="--kc:#9376B3">
        <div class="key-badge mono">E</div>
        <div class="key-color-bar"></div>
        <div class="key-color-name mono">Purple</div>
        <h3 class="key-range">High King's Territory → EADal Shore</h3>
        <p class="key-desc">Summit to The Darkive. Where the Brush replaces the Sword. Rivers across E converge into one triangular body at the edge.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="key-card" style="--kc:#F09021">
        <div class="key-badge mono">B</div>
        <div class="key-color-bar"></div>
        <div class="key-color-name mono">Orange</div>
        <h3 class="key-range">The Wha → Dewdrop Lake</h3>
        <p class="key-desc">River corridor to lake edge. Splits Niap into left and right hemispheres. The Corridor of Return. The Enway made geographic.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="key-card" style="--kc:#45B7C8">
        <div class="key-badge mono">F</div>
        <div class="key-color-bar"></div>
        <div class="key-color-name mono">Blue</div>
        <h3 class="key-range">Fairidge → Fairface</h3>
        <p class="key-desc">Ridge climb to tectonic anchor. F and F# create the Fenning axis — F descends, F# ascends. Both point at Piralus. The Enway made stone.</p>
      </div>

    </div>

    <div class="keys-label mono" style="margin-top:3rem;">Sharp keys — exhale (5)</div>
    <div class="keys-grid">

      <div class="key-card" style="--kc:#80CEE0">
        <div class="key-badge mono">F#</div>
        <div class="key-color-bar"></div>
        <div class="key-color-name mono">Sky</div>
        <h3 class="key-range">Harvestview Top → Niap City</h3>
        <p class="key-desc">Mountain viewpoint to starting city. Where you wake up — you do not arrive. Stan Dalone's RIFT Store. The starting key on the Color Cycler.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="key-card" style="--kc:#9B4F3A">
        <div class="key-badge mono">C#</div>
        <div class="key-color-bar"></div>
        <div class="key-color-name mono">Brick</div>
        <h3 class="key-range">Reed Krap / Hoyle Face Shin → Squish / Dunge</h3>
        <p class="key-desc">Rain shadow country. Two interior landmarks split by neighboring keys: Reed Krap nearest F#, Hoyle Face Shin nearest G#. Mas Psci's territory.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="key-card" style="--kc:#84C44E">
        <div class="key-badge mono">G#</div>
        <div class="key-color-bar"></div>
        <div class="key-color-name mono">Lime</div>
        <h3 class="key-range">Mystery Camp → Eyer Land</h3>
        <p class="key-desc">The Unknown to the islands. Named for the experience of being lost. Ireland + eye + eyre + island — the foreigners who came for familiar landscapes.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="key-card" style="--kc:#B5338A">
        <div class="key-badge mono">D#</div>
        <div class="key-color-bar"></div>
        <div class="key-color-name mono">Magenta</div>
        <h3 class="key-range">Steampipes → Steambridge</h3>
        <p class="key-desc">Eastern approach. The Steam key — the prefix carries you the whole way. Steamford (the city beyond) is the backdrop.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="key-card" style="--kc:#D4B483">
        <div class="key-badge mono">A#</div>
        <div class="key-color-bar"></div>
        <div class="key-color-name mono">Tan</div>
        <h3 class="key-range">A##A A##A → The Steam Yards</h3>
        <p class="key-desc">Absurd interior to shipyards. Always twice, always unreadable. Don'te is the backdrop beyond. Between Trip's lighthouse and the river crossing.</p>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="usic-order">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="order-block">
      <div class="order-label mono">Circle of 5ths (ascending)</div>
      <div class="order-keys mono">C → G → D → A → E → B → F# → C# → G# → D# → A# → F</div>
    </div>
    <div class="order-block">
      <div class="order-label mono">NEST week schedule</div>
      <div class="order-keys mono">F → C → G → D → A → E → B → F# → C# → G# → D# → A#</div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="usic-provenance">
  <div class="container">
    <p class="prov-text">The name doesn't create the place. The place creates the name.</p>
    <p class="prov-meta mono">Waywood Principle #1</p>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
.usic-hero{padding:6rem 0 4rem;background:linear-gradient(160deg,#1a2e28 0%,var(--forest) 60%);border-bottom:2px solid var(--teal);}
.usic-eyebrow{font-size:0.6rem;letter-spacing:0.3em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--teal);margin-bottom:0.75rem;}
.usic-title{font-family:var(--font-head);font-size:clamp(3rem,8vw,5rem);color:var(--warm-white);line-height:1;margin-bottom:1.25rem;letter-spacing:-0.02em;}
.usic-sub{font-size:1.05rem;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.7);max-width:580px;line-height:1.8;}

.usic-center{padding:3rem 0;background:var(--off-white);}
.piralus-card{max-width:600px;margin:0 auto;text-align:center;padding:2rem;border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:var(--radius);background:var(--card-bg);}
.piralus-label{font-size:0.6rem;letter-spacing:0.25em;color:var(--muted);margin-bottom:0.5rem;}
.piralus-name{font-family:var(--font-head);font-size:2rem;color:var(--forest);margin-bottom:0.75rem;}
.piralus-desc{font-size:0.95rem;color:var(--text-lt);line-height:1.7;}

.usic-keys{padding:4rem 0;}
.keys-label{font-size:0.6rem;letter-spacing:0.25em;color:var(--forest);margin-bottom:1.5rem;text-transform:uppercase;}
.keys-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fill,minmax(300px,1fr));gap:1.25rem;}

.key-card{background:var(--card-bg);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:var(--radius);padding:1.5rem;position:relative;overflow:hidden;}
.key-badge{position:absolute;top:1rem;right:1rem;font-size:1.5rem;font-weight:700;color:var(--kc);opacity:0.3;}
.key-color-bar{height:3px;width:60px;background:var(--kc);border-radius:2px;margin-bottom:0.75rem;}
.key-color-name{font-size:0.6rem;letter-spacing:0.15em;color:var(--kc);margin-bottom:0.5rem;}
.key-range{font-family:var(--font-head);font-size:1.1rem;color:var(--text);margin-bottom:0.5rem;line-height:1.4;}
.key-desc{font-size:0.85rem;color:var(--text-lt);line-height:1.7;}

.usic-order{padding:3rem 0;background:var(--off-white);}
.order-block{margin-bottom:1.5rem;}
.order-label{font-size:0.6rem;letter-spacing:0.2em;color:var(--muted);margin-bottom:0.5rem;}
.order-keys{font-size:0.85rem;color:var(--forest);letter-spacing:0.05em;}

.usic-provenance{padding:4rem 0;background:var(--forest);text-align:center;}
.prov-text{font-family:var(--font-head);font-size:clamp(1.2rem,2.5vw,1.65rem);color:var(--warm-white);font-style:italic;margin-bottom:1rem;max-width:700px;margin-left:auto;margin-right:auto;line-height:1.65;}
.prov-meta{font-size:0.6rem;letter-spacing:0.2em;color:var(--teal);}
</style>
</BaseLayout>
